<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrīmaccāḷukya vikramavariśada 43
<lb n="2" break="no"/>neya viḷaṁbhisaṁvatsarada bhādrapada puṇname
<lb n="3"/>Ādityavārada(ṁ)ndu <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> bharatēsvaradēvara kammā
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ṟikeya dasavandava gaṁgayana kētōjanu gaṁ
<lb n="5" break="no"/>ganuṁ dēvargge kālugacci koṭṭaru mahime
<lb n="6"/>mannaṇe poṟagu koṇḍa gadyāṇa A
<lb n="7" break="no"/>ydu Antappudakke sākṣi nūṟippatto
<lb n="8" break="no"/>kkalu <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g>
</p>

